## 360Ghar Backend — Project Overview

- Entrypoint FastAPI app: [app/main.py](mdc:app/main.py)
- API router aggregation: [app/api/api_v1/api.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/api.py)
- Async DB session dependency: [app/core/database.py](mdc:app/core/database.py) → `get_db()` yields `AsyncSession` with auto commit/rollback.
- Authentication helpers: [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/auth.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/auth.py) → `get_current_active_user`, `get_current_user_optional`.
- Supabase token verification: [app/core/security.py](mdc:app/core/security.py) → `verify_supabase_token()` (non-blocking via anyio thread pool).
- Caching layer and helpers: [app/core/cache.py](mdc:app/core/cache.py) → `cache_manager`, `PropertyCacheManager`.

### Layered Architecture
- API layer (FastAPI endpoints): [app/api/](mdc:app/api/)
- Schemas (Pydantic models): [app/schemas/](mdc:app/schemas/)
- Services (business logic): [app/services/](mdc:app/services/)
- Repositories (DB access): [app/repositories/](mdc:app/repositories/)
- Models (SQLAlchemy ORM): [app/models/](mdc:app/models/)

### Common Navigation
- Properties endpoints and filters: [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/properties.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/properties.py)
- Swipe endpoints and service: [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/swipes.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/swipes.py), [app/services/swipe.py](mdc:app/services/swipe.py)
- Visits & Bookings: [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/visits.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/visits.py), [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/bookings.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/bookings.py)

### Running the app
- Dev server: `python run.py` or `uvicorn app.main:app --reload`

